Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:20.87,Signs,,0,0,0,,Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.42,0:00:02.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:07.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fun season where you can enjoy yourself going to the sea, the mountains, or under the dazzling sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:11.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you never know where danger may lurk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fun vacation might take a sudden turn into terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.04,0:00:20.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today, let's play back the case where I went to the beach with Ran and Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:24.06,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Flowers dance to a piano's rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:25.83,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Two people face-to-face are a mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:27.83,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A summer beach and a lovely encounter,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:30.30,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but a suspicious man foreshadows a case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.05,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:33.90,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:36.28,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:26.83,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Izu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:39.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sonoko! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Photographing your butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with a photo like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna show it to Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} when he gets back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:53.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think how happy he'll be!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly. Shin'ichi isn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:01.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:03.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:06.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does a little kid know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:10.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ugh... I can't {\i1}wait{\i0} to get back to normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've been acting weird, Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why're you picking on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:16.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just a bit jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:21.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Why? Did I do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:23.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't you noticed, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:27.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why'd we come on a weekend beach trip to Izu in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For you, it's your usual man-hunting trip, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:36.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's a carefully planned "poor girl vacation", too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:45.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We always stay at my family's summer house, or an expensive hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Oh, {\i1}how{\i0} can I talk to a girl who's so far beyond my reach?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, we're staying at an old inn, where we can reel in unexpecting boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:59.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Some plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the train here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:12.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the fireworks show last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even at this beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of the guys are after you. Every single one of them, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on... No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:30.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll just show Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} a photo of you in your underwear that I took last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:32.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:34.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't even think about it, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you do that, I'll never forgive you for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:43.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just kidding. Never took any photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For crying out loud, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:47.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, she was lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:55.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to get some lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:56.85,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tadahiko Michiwaki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's on me, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:59.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes! We'd love...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want {\i1}her{\i0}, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:07.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, take her! She's in season!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't try anything funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's already taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was kinda hoping to get to know {\i1}you{\i0} better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:20.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did it, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:27.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Impossible. This is Sonoko we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:35.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There has to be something behind this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:39.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've {\i1}got{\i0} to stop thinking like a detective all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:40.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and I will stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:56.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a student at Beika University, Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran's dad used to study there, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:00.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:06.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come on. Always talking about guys and then she wimped out and dragged us along. {probably wrong}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what brings you to Izu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a trip to heal a broken heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My girlfriend dumped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was gazing into the sea in despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...when an angel appeared before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a hunch you're the goddess who's going to save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:34.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's your draft beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:49.47,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Makoto Kyogoku
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir, please don't drop cigarette butts all over the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're a pain to clean up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:57.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't we seen that waiter somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:07:02.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course we have. His dad owns the inn where we're staying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's come to help over summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was staring at us from the front steps of the inn, so I asked one of the workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:16.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why's he working {\i1}here{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably run by the same person who takes care of Kawaraya Inn, where we're staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:25.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? You're staying at Kawaraya Inn?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:27.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fancy that, it's right next to my hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how about we all have dinner at a fancy restaurant by the sea tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:38.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll pick you up in my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't forget to bring your camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:44.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just learned this from a local,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:50.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there was an incident at the beach near the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:56.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About a year ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:08:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a girl with long brown hair was stabbed repeatedly in the stomach and killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:09.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was killed on her way to that restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:12.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there were no witnesses. The police are still looking for the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a year since the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so most people forgot about it, and the restaurant's doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, she seems to have taken a liking to that restaurant, and still drops by...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She appears in photos taken inside the restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:36.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...as a grotesque ghost with her innards pouring out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:40.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So let's see if she really appears in a photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:50.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what do you think? I still have about ten shots left in my camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Don't even bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:57.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if we showed it to Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, he might notice something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:09:01.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, we're going to show him the {\i1}shocking{\i0} photo, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the point of showing him that one? You can't even tell who it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could figure it out with his super deductive skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deductive skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:17.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her boyfriend's a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:18.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what's in that photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:22.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:23.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:26.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's your yakisoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got a lot of customers waiting, so hurry up and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, what's with that waiter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does he have a grudge against us or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:43.47,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shoji Terabayashi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't we eat somewhere other than that restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sounds creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:50.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ghost thing's just a rumor, and it's been a year since the murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the dead woman got bored of that restaurant by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They found another one in the forest by the train tracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:05.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A corpse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bloody corpse of a woman with brown hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stabbed multiple times in the abdominal area.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:37.19,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Detective Yokomizo\NShizuoka Police Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:37.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like another tourist, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, what's the time of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Between 8 and 9 PM last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:50.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was right after the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:55.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that around the time we passed by here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way you'll be attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But look at me! I have brown hair too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no guarantee I won't be next!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:15.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:19.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not with my whole life ahead of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:25.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you as long as you're here in Izu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I guess we should change our dinner reservations, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And no cameras!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:39.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll pick you up around 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:41.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait for me in front of the inn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:43.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:50.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wasn't that guy at the seafood place, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should go back to change clothes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it isn't Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you've come to Izu, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we came for the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:13.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, is Detective Mouri here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:16.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's just us three.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're the knight accompanying these two damsels, huh, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:26.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be sure to protect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:29.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:32.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you can see, we've had a troubling incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:36.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll be leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give Detective Mouri my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's as cheerful as always, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's not having any luck, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If your dad was here, he'd solve the case in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:13:00.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Detective Yokomizo is {\i1}far{\i0} more competent than the old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:19.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's starting to rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:23.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} shows up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:28.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hero always appears at the last second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop! You're embarrassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:39.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with the umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:41.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess he wants us to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's got a crush on you, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:49.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're getting popular, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:52.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not the dark guy too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:55.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, you already have Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:59.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Ran, you're making me blush...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap. I left my purse in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, I'll be back in a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:05.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:22.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}know{\i0} I've seen the guy in glasses somewhere, but where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:24.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhere in this inn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhere else...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where? Where'd you see him, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:54.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's taking you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's changing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:28.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A weird guy jumped me... he escaped through the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:39.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn... He's already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why would anybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:45.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:50.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I opened the door, there was a guy searching our bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tried to shout, and he grabbed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:55.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Searching our bags?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he was trying to steal our underwear! Yuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:16:01.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did he look like? You saw his face, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never had the chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was pitch dark in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:08.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how do you know it's a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bit his arm in the struggle. It was hairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:15.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Way to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are the lights out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:22.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:28.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My car broke down on the way here, so I ran here as fast as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how'd you find our room?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find you two outside, so I asked one of the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:40.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His shirt's wet and his pants are muddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:41.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What if...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you mind taking your shirt off?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you could show me your upper arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:50.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anything wrong with my arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:59.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Nothing. No tooth marks from Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Happy now, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:02.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:06.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:10.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A bandage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to your right arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:17.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had a little struggle with a drunk customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When was that? Please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:25.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think it was him. The guy who attacked me was hairier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. A man came in through this window, ransacked our bags,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:34.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and attacked Sonoko when she happened to walk in on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he ran off as soon as he heard us coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:42.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must've been a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:44.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've had this happen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:47.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did? Then why didn't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:53.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}did{\i0} tell you to make sure to lock up, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.48,0:18:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Walking around in a midriff top at this time of night, what are you expecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're practically {\i1}asking{\i0} to be attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't even look good on you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:12.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my favorite top, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You look good in anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:18.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yukata, swimsuit, whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to move you. There's another room open.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless you want to spend the night in the room where you were attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd also advise you not to go out, and have dinner here at the inn instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:43.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You never know if that man might be waiting for you outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do we do, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll eat here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The food's much better than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:04.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we'd known this before, we would've eaten here last night, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:09.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We would've been able to get you a nicer meal if you'd made reservations in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:13.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, the meal's on the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...if you don't spread any "rumors" about a thief lurking around the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:24.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right! Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't mention the underwear thief who pulled a knife on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:29.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! I saw it shining in the light coming through the side screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:38.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was sharp and gleaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.14,0:19:40.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Uh-oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:46.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What if our thief is the same man who killed the woman found in the woods today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:54.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Supposedly a year ago, here in Izu, a brown-haired woman was stabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:59.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But why would the killer target Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:02.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just because she has brown hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:09.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The guy who attacked Sonoko ransacked her belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:15.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's one thing in her luggage that could be connected to the murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:17.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:21.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe one of the photos captured something related to the murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:25.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}! Did the guy who attacked you steal your camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was still in my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.94,0:20:30.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the compartment where I had it {\i1}was{\i0} open.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:32.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he stole the film?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I finished off all thirty-six photos, so I dropped it off to get it developed at noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:40.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought we could look at the pictures over dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? I've got the photos here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:46.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mind if I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:50.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I kept that special photo of you for safe-keeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:59.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know all of these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:02.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seem to have interrupted a lot of lovers...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:05.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko was all cranky before she met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She kept pranking all the couples we met!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:10.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:15.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Strange... There's nothing odd about the photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:17.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I don't see the victim, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:24.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We {\i1}did{\i0} pass through the forest where the body was found last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:27.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but Sonoko didn't take any photo then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:36.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So what made the killer think Sonoko'd taken an incriminating photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:39.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.62,0:21:45.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe someone overheard her at lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:50.74,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He could figure it out with his super deductive skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:55.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The killer could've been in the seafood shop at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.82,0:21:59.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But was it really {\i1}that{\i0} suspicious a remark?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:03.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're going home tomorrow at noon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:04.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how about we stop by the cursed restaurant in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.92,0:22:11.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't be as scary in the daylight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But no cameras!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I imagining things, or does this guy keep watching us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:29.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And what about that guy in the glasses, the one Ran thinks she's seen before?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:33.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And as for the guy who attacked Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.38,0:22:37.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Was he really just a simple thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.44,0:24:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.35,0:24:09.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s car?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.48,0:24:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's heading straight for a cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.90,0:24:12.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko! Wake up, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.90,0:24:16.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.53,0:24:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you thought you could run away forever, then you were wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.20,0:24:22.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, damn! Sonoko's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.74,0:24:27.71,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.71,0:24:32.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Pantograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.71,0:24:34.62,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That's the black and white thing that's famous in China...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.62,0:24:37.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's not a panda, it's that thing on top of an electric train!
